highlights.text: Taylor Swift has the most spots on Top Songs USA. “Fortnight (feat. Post Malone)” is the highest at #1.
“No Role Modelz” by J. Cole has been on Top Songs USA the longest, at 205 weeks straight.
“Us Vs. Them” by $uicideboy$ is the biggest gainer on Top Songs USA, up 65 spots at #77.
“Fortnight (feat. Post Malone)” by Taylor Swift and Post Malone is the highest new entry on Top Songs USA at #1.
